1
00:01:00,920 --> 00:01:01,719
The war is over.

2
00:01:02,640 --> 00:01:03,240
Go home.

3
00:01:06,120 --> 00:01:06,840
Go home.

4
00:01:14,640 --> 00:01:15,200
Yan Ying,

5
00:01:17,280 --> 00:01:18,680
why haven't you woken up yet?

6
00:01:21,519 --> 00:01:23,599
Have you seen the ending I rewrote for you?

7
00:01:26,599 --> 00:01:29,200
Have you seen the people you protected return to Qingyun State?

8
00:01:35,680 --> 00:01:37,959
Have you seen the cakes you like to eat?

9
00:01:47,920 --> 00:01:49,000
I regret it.

10
00:01:50,280 --> 00:01:53,120
I regret writing about hatred and separation,

11
00:01:54,000 --> 00:01:55,719
ambition and greed,

12
00:01:56,000 --> 00:01:57,400
hatred and betrayal.

13
00:01:58,560 --> 00:01:59,799
I regret my pessimism about human nature.

14
00:01:59,799 --> 00:02:01,640
to end this book with

15
00:02:01,640 --> 00:02:03,359
this war tragedy.

16
00:02:05,120 --> 00:02:05,840
Yan Ying,

17
00:02:06,640 --> 00:02:09,240
your sincerity and courage changed my mind

18
00:02:09,879 --> 00:02:11,400
and everything.

19
00:02:14,719 --> 00:02:15,319
I promise you

20
00:02:16,439 --> 00:02:18,639
I will give you the best ending.

21
00:02:24,120 --> 00:02:24,400
Hey.

22
00:02:28,639 --> 00:02:29,319
How did

23
00:02:29,759 --> 00:02:30,599
the war end?

24
00:02:33,039 --> 00:02:33,960
During the blood moon,

25
00:02:34,280 --> 00:02:35,039
the twin stars fell.

26
00:02:36,080 --> 00:02:37,479
It's the power of the Star Chart

27
00:02:37,680 --> 00:02:38,680
that turned the tide of war.

28
00:02:39,240 --> 00:02:40,840
The fate of the twin stars falls upon us,

29
00:02:41,400 --> 00:02:42,400
making us live and die together.

30
00:02:44,960 --> 00:02:46,159
I will never hurt you again.

31
00:02:51,080 --> 00:02:52,599
Now I will ascend to the throne.

32
00:02:53,520 --> 00:02:54,599
The view from the top is beautiful.

33
00:02:56,520 --> 00:02:57,039
Yan Ying,

34
00:02:57,919 --> 00:02:59,000
be my empress.

35
00:03:06,800 --> 00:03:08,280
I will always be your comrade-in-arms,

36
00:03:09,000 --> 00:03:09,800
your fellow soldier,

37
00:03:11,439 --> 00:03:12,759
but not your empress.

38
00:03:13,360 --> 00:03:13,840
Why?

39
00:03:16,159 --> 00:03:16,680
Cheng Jing,

40
00:03:18,280 --> 00:03:19,680
our relationship

41
00:03:20,599 --> 00:03:21,560
is predestined,

42
00:03:22,439 --> 00:03:23,240
not real.

43
00:03:24,879 --> 00:03:25,759
What do you mean?

44
00:03:26,199 --> 00:03:27,120
It's hard for you

45
00:03:27,800 --> 00:03:29,000
to understand.

46
00:03:31,080 --> 00:03:32,599
Just imagine that someone in heaven

47
00:03:32,879 --> 00:03:34,280
has written our fate

48
00:03:35,000 --> 00:03:35,840
and arranged for us

49
00:03:36,120 --> 00:03:37,080
to be here today.

50
00:03:38,680 --> 00:03:39,639
But feelings

51
00:03:40,000 --> 00:03:40,879
can't be arranged.

52
00:03:42,599 --> 00:03:43,439
One day,

53
00:03:43,800 --> 00:03:44,479
you will understand.

54
00:03:45,520 --> 00:03:46,319
At that time,

55
00:03:46,639 --> 00:03:48,439
you won't be obsessed with our current relationship.

56
00:03:48,639 --> 00:03:49,319
I don't understand.

57
00:03:50,879 --> 00:03:52,240
I only know that you can't leave me.

58
00:03:53,280 --> 00:03:53,639
Look,

59
00:03:55,280 --> 00:03:57,520
this is the peaceful era we've fought for with blood and sweat.

60
00:03:58,639 --> 00:03:59,560
Do you really want to give it up?

61
00:04:01,080 --> 00:04:02,479
The peace and prosperity of this era

62
00:04:03,080 --> 00:04:03,960
will replace me

63
00:04:05,719 --> 00:04:06,919
to accompany you.

64
00:04:15,879 --> 00:04:16,360
Yan Ying,

65
00:04:20,879 --> 00:04:22,040
I won't let you go.

66
00:04:23,000 --> 00:04:23,800
No matter where you go,

67
00:04:24,519 --> 00:04:25,360
I'll find you.

68
00:04:28,800 --> 00:04:29,879
I couldn't bear to tell you

69
00:04:30,439 --> 00:04:32,160
that our world was just a dream.

70
00:04:32,639 --> 00:04:33,160
But

71
00:04:33,680 --> 00:04:35,160
at least it was a beautiful dream.

72
00:05:47,519 --> 00:05:48,160
Wipe it off.

73
00:05:48,319 --> 00:05:49,240
How long has it been since you washed your face?

74
00:06:41,560 --> 00:06:42,759
In the end,

75
00:06:42,920 --> 00:06:44,319
Xiao Chengjing and Yan Ying,

76
00:06:44,319 --> 00:06:46,399
as twin stars with intertwined fates,

77
00:06:46,759 --> 00:06:48,560
was turned around by the Qixi star chart.

78
00:06:49,639 --> 00:06:50,519
Xiao Chengjing let go of his hatred

79
00:06:50,920 --> 00:06:52,920
and his betrayal of you

80
00:06:53,319 --> 00:06:54,759
was no longer there.

81
00:06:55,040 --> 00:06:56,800
The war was over,

82
00:06:57,560 --> 00:06:58,480
and Xiao Chengjing ascended to the throne

83
00:06:58,839 --> 00:07:00,120
and brought peace to the world.

84
00:07:00,240 --> 00:07:01,120
General Yan Ying,

85
00:07:01,319 --> 00:07:02,879
the protector of the state,

86
00:07:03,079 --> 00:07:05,800
accidentally deciphered the secret of the mysterious Qixi star chart

87
00:07:06,079 --> 00:07:07,360
and went to another world.

88
00:07:07,879 --> 00:07:08,360
It's up to her

89
00:07:08,680 --> 00:07:10,000
to decide

90
00:07:10,240 --> 00:07:12,000
what kind of story she wants to tell.

91
00:07:14,319 --> 00:07:14,800
Hmm.

92
00:07:16,319 --> 00:07:18,000
Then I need to think carefully

93
00:07:18,120 --> 00:07:20,279
about how to write my story.

94
00:07:43,920 --> 00:07:45,920
From my years of experience in marching,

95
00:07:46,279 --> 00:07:47,199
it seems you haven't broken any bones.

96
00:07:48,319 --> 00:07:49,000
But

97
00:07:49,399 --> 00:07:51,199
it takes a hundred days to heal a serious injury.

98
00:07:51,879 --> 00:07:53,040
I'll wrap it a bit tighter for you.

99
00:07:53,800 --> 00:07:54,560
After that,

100
00:07:54,920 --> 00:07:56,040
you can't move around too much.

101
00:07:57,360 --> 00:07:57,800
Yes, sir.

102
00:07:58,000 --> 00:07:58,680
General,

103
00:08:01,680 --> 00:08:02,639
I'm still not satisfied

104
00:08:03,040 --> 00:08:04,399
with this novel.

105
00:08:05,240 --> 00:08:06,240
What else do you want to change?

106
00:08:06,240 --> 00:08:07,279
Of course,

107
00:08:07,439 --> 00:08:09,279
he can eat spicy food.

108
00:08:15,560 --> 00:08:16,160
Oh,

109
00:08:16,399 --> 00:08:17,040
why don't you change it?

110
00:08:18,920 --> 00:08:21,240
Changing the character's setting in the novel

111
00:08:22,000 --> 00:08:24,040
is somewhat cheating.

112
00:08:24,439 --> 00:08:25,199
Besides,

113
00:08:25,600 --> 00:08:26,279
I think

114
00:08:26,560 --> 00:08:28,160
You're perfect as you are.

115
00:08:29,480 --> 00:08:31,079
I like the me in your stories,

116
00:08:31,839 --> 00:08:32,960
the me on the battlefield,

117
00:08:33,159 --> 00:08:34,039
the me who can't eat spicy food.

118
00:08:35,399 --> 00:08:36,200
I like all of them.

119
00:08:39,720 --> 00:08:40,519
I like you too.

120
00:08:44,080 --> 00:08:44,840
You can like me.

121
00:08:50,440 --> 00:08:52,440
My homeland is at peace.

122
00:08:53,039 --> 00:08:55,000
I choose to come to the real world.

123
00:08:56,480 --> 00:08:57,840
I don't know where the future is

124
00:08:58,279 --> 00:08:59,440
or how long I can stay here.

125
00:09:00,519 --> 00:09:02,000
But I will cherish

126
00:09:02,279 --> 00:09:03,879
every day with you.
